  "texts": [
    "However, along with the increase in the total number of documents published over time, open-access documents got doubled between 2017 and 2023.",
    "As shown in Fig. 2, there is a noticeable growth in the total number of documents published from 2017 to 2023 in the subject area.",
    "From 2017 to 2022, there has been a gradual increase in the number of documents that were published, indicating a growth of 189.8 %.",
    "The data presented for 2023 is not complete as it was collected during the middle of the year (June 22, 2023).",
    "However, the reported number of 72 documents signifies promising growth."
  ]
}